      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. It was narrated to me by Muhammad b. al-Hassan from Muhammad b. al-Hassan al-Saffar from al-Abbas b. Ma’ruf from al-Hassan b. Mahbub from Ali b. Ziyad from a man from Abi Abdillah (a.s.) who said: “I guarantee that one who leaves the house wearing a turban will return safe and sound to his family.”"
        ]
